Le said that the suspect also stole $60 from his wallet.

The Harris County Sheriff's Office Safe Home Task Force is now hoping to identify the suspect, who is described as a Hispanic male between 16 and 18 years old.

He was wearing a New Era baseball cap with a San Antonio Spurs logo on the brim and has a tattoo behind his right ear, possibly of Asian characters.

